\ip ∆ók…®tabh â k…®n â chandikirw…® na Maaroko. Maaroko aar…® arabhirikirwa Yoohana Maaroko. Aar…® w âmw…® wa Abhakiriisit â bhe embere (\xt Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 12:12).\xt* Amang ºana gan â aandikir…® m âk…®tabh â k…®n â akagamenya bhwaheene, k â k âbha, aar…® arahirana na abharwazi ncha Paaur â (\xt Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 13:1‚Äë13\xt*), Bharinaabha (\xt Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 15:36‚Äë41\xt*) na Peetero (\xt 1 Peetero 5:13\xt*). 
\ip M âk…®tabh â k…®n â, Maaroko aar…® araand…®k…®ra Abhakiriisit â bh â  âr âbh…®ri rwa Ruumi. Ribhaga riyo Neero newe aar…®  âm ât…®mi wa Ruumi, na kwar…® n…® …®nyaak â k âBhakiriisit â. Maaroko akeenda kokong ºya Abhakiriisit â mubhwisirirya kwa k âbhabh â âr…®ra, bhareenderwa k ânyaakibhwa ch…®mbu Kiriisit â aanyaakiibhw…® na kukwa. 
\ip Maaroko areerecha amiis…®…®gi gu ukwand…®ka …®k…®tabh â k…®n â k âr âk…®r…®r…® rwe embere, 
\ipq ‚Äú∆óng ºana ∆ónz âmu ig âr â wa Y…®…®su Kiriisit â, Umwana wa Mungu.‚Äù 
\im Areenda abhas âmi bhaaz…® bhamenye k âbha, Y…®…®su newe Kiriisit â, w ân â Mungu aatumir…® ch…®mbu aarag…®…®n ºy…®. M âk…®tabh â k…®n â, Maaroko aragamb…®ra amaaru gan â Y…®…®su aar…® arakora k âk…®ra gan â aar…® akurwaza. Maaroko akaand…®ka ebherenjo na amagan â g…® …®bh…®s…®g â …®bh…®nd…® bh…®n â Y…®…®su aak ârir…®. Y…®…®su akahorya abhaat â, akaruusha amasambwa na k âbhabheerera abhaat â  âbh âbh…® bhwabh â. Gayo gareerekan ºya  âbh ânaja bhwa Y…®…®su, k âbha akarwa kwa Mungu, akaaza na kuhurucha  âbh âh âru bhwaz…® kwa k âbharuusha abhaat â kurwa muzinguru z â  âbh âbh…®. 
\c 1  
\s1 Yoohana arakonza …®nz…®ra ig âr â wa Y…®…®su 
\r (Mataayo 3:1‚Äë12; Ruuka 3:1‚Äë18; Yoohana 1:19‚Äë28) 
\p  
\v 1 Bh ân â nebhwe  âbh âtang…® bhw…® ∆óng ºana ∆ónz âmu ig âr â wa Y…®…®su Kiriisit â,\f + \fr 1:1a \fk Kiriisit â\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* Umwana wa Mungu.\f + \fr 1:1b \fk Umwana wa Mungu\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* 
\v 2 Ch…®mbu yandikirw…® n â  âm âr â ât…®r…®ri Isaaya m âk…®tabh â chaz…® k âbha, Mungu akabhuga, ‚ÄúRora, n…®rat âma umutumwa waan…® m âbh âtang…® bhwaz â, w ân â araakokonzere …®nz…®ra.\f + \fr 1:2 \xt Rora Maraaki 3:1.\f* 
\v 3 Umutumwa w ân â n…®‚Äëw ân â ak âragan ºya mwit…®r…®g â, ‚ÄòMokore …®nz…®ra y â …Ñm âk âr â, mogorore …®bh…®h…®t â bhyaz…®!‚Äô‚Ää‚Äù\f + \fr 1:3 \xt Rora Isaaya 40:3.\f* 
\p  
\v 4 Umutumwa wuyo aar…® arabhirikirwa Yoohana. Aar…® mwit…®r…®g â ararwaz…®ra abhaat â k âbha, bhatig…®  âbh âbh…® n â  âk âbhatiizwa, korereke Mungu abhabheerere  âbh âbh…® bhwabh â.  
\v 5 Abhaat â bhaaru kurwa k âr âbh…®ri rwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu na muchar â ch âsi cha Yudeya, bhaar…® bharaja kwa Yoohana. Bhakatiga  âbh âbh…® bhwabh â, akabhabhatiiza m âk…®taar â cha Yorodaani. 
\p  
\v 6 Yoohana aar…® ibh âhir…®  âbh âz â âk…® bhw…® …®ngamiya, no omokena gwa riseero mukiribhizi.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft Zengebho z…®n â Yoohana aar…® akwibhoha, zaar…® ncha z â  âm âr â ât…®r…®ri ∆ó…®riya. \xt Rora 2 Abhat…®mi 1:8.\f* Ibhyakurya bhyaz…® bhyar…® zingig…® nu ubhw âk…® bhwa mwit…®r…®g â. 
\p  
\v 7 Aar…® ararwaza arabhuga, ‚ÄúHan â n…®k âmara iny…®, araaza  âm â ât â w â  âbh ânaja k ânk…®ra. N…®takwenderwa n â âr â kwihiinya k âtaz âra zisiri zi ibhikw…®ra bhyaz…®.\f + \fr 1:7 \ft Ar…®…®bh…® umugini arasik…®ra munyumba, mb â âsa wi iyaas…® bh âk âng ºu aar…® aramuruusha ibhikw…®ra na kwoja amag âr â gaaz…®.\f* 
\v 8 Iny…® n…®rabhabhatiiza kwa amanzi, nawe ewe arabhabhatiiza kwe Ekoro ∆ónd…®ndu.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:8 \fk Ekoro ∆ónd…®ndu\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* 
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhatiizwa no okogemwa mwit…®r…®g â 
\r (Mataayo 3:13‚Äì4:11; Ruuka 3:21‚Äë22, 4:1‚Äë13) 
\p  
\v 9 Ribhaga riyo, Y…®…®su akaaza kurwa m âr âbh…®ri rwa Nazar…®…®ti, muchar â cha Gariraaya. W â âsi Yoohana akam âbhatiiza m âk…®taar â cha Yorodaani.  
\v 10 Han â Y…®…®su aar…® aratiira kurwa m âmanzi, akarora risaar â ririig âka, ne Ekoro ∆ónd…®ndu iriika kwewe nchi ikiguuti.  
\v 11 Riraka kurwa mwisaar â r…®kabhuga, ‚ÄúAw…® ni‚ÄëMwana waan…®  âm âs…®…®gwa, n…®z âm…®r…®…®rw…® na naaw…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Hayohayo Ekoro ∆ónd…®ndu …®kam âkangata Y…®…®su kuja mwit…®r…®g â.  
\v 13 Akiikara iyo sik â merongo ene, aragemwa na Sh…®taani.\f + \fr 1:13a \fk Sh…®taani\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* Aar…® hamw…®mw…® ni ibhity…®nyi bhya mwit…®r…®g â, na bhamaraika\f + \fr 1:13b \fk Bhamaraika\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora ring ºana \ft \+it maraika\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* bha Mungu bhaar…® bharamwangar…®ra. 
\s1 Y…®…®su aratanga korobhora abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® 
\r (Mataayo 4:12‚Äë22; Ruuka 4:14‚Äë15, 5:1‚Äë11) 
\p  
\v 14 Z…®kah…®ta sik â nzaru, Yoohana akabhohwa. Han â aar…® mokebhoho, Y…®…®su akaja muchar â cha Gariraaya, aar…® ararwaza ∆óng ºana ∆ónz âmu ya Mungu.  
\v 15 Aar…® arabhuga, ‚ÄúRibhaga r…®n â ryar â ât âr…®…®rw…® rihikir…®, n â  âbh ât…®mi bhwa Mungu\f + \fr 1:15 \fk …Ñbh ât…®mi bhwa Mungu\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* bh âraariir…®. Mmbe, mutig…®  âbh âbh…® bhwanyu, mwisiriry…® ∆óng ºana ∆ónz âmu yiyo.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Rusik â r âmw…®, han â Y…®…®su aar…® ak âh…®ta rusiz â w…® …®nyanza ya Gariraaya, akarora Sim â âni nu umunyi waaz…® Andureya. Bhaar…® bhararekera zenzero m ânyanza, k â k âbha bhaar…® abhaw…®s…®ni.  
\v 17 Y…®…®su akabhabh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúMuntun…® na niiny…® n…®rabhakora k âbha abhaw…®s…®ni bha abhaat â.‚Äù  
\v 18 Hayohayo, bhakazitiga zenzero zaabh â, bhakatuna Y…®…®su. 
\p  
\v 19 Y…®…®su akaja embere hamw…®mw…® na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhabh…®r…®. Akarora Yaakobho nu umunyi waaz…® Yoohana abhaana bha Zebhedaayo, bhaar…® mubhwat â bharazomya zenzero zaabh â.  
\v 20 Ribhaga riyoriyo, akabhabh…®r…®k…®ra bhamutun…®, bhabh…® abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®. Bhakatiga wiis…® hamw…®mw…® na abhahocha bhaaz…® mubhwat â, bhakatuna Y…®…®su. 
\s1 Y…®…®su areerecha  âbh ânaja bhwaz…® 
\r (Ruuka 4:31‚Äë37) 
\p  
\v 21 Neho Y…®…®su na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhane, bhakaja m âr âbh…®ri rwa Kap…®rinaumu. Han â urusik â rw â  âbh ât â âr â\f + \fr 1:21a \fk Urusik â rw â  âbh ât â âr â\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* rwahikir…®, bhakasik…®ra mwirwaz…®r â,\f + \fr 1:21b \fk Rirwaz…®r â\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* Y…®…®su akatanga kwija.  
\v 22 Amiija gaaz…® gakabharuguurya abhaat â bh â âsi bhan â bhaar…® bharamwitegeerera. Aar…® ariija nch â  âm â ât â w â  âbh ânaja, na …®taar…® ch…®mbu abhiija bhaabh â bhi imigir â\f + \fr 1:22 \fk Abhiija bhi imigir â\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* ja Musa bhahiija. 
\p  
\v 23 Mwirwaz…®r â ryabh â, mwar…® n â  âm â ât â w ân â aar…® na risambwa. Akatiirya riraka,  
\v 24 arabhuga, ‚ÄúAw…® Y…®…®su wa Nazar…®…®ti,  âtat ânyaacha! Nang â, wiizir…® kuturicha? Nikw…®z…® aw…® n…®‚Äëw…®…®w…®, aw…® n…®‚ÄëM âr…®ndu wa Mungu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 25 Y…®…®su akar…®haar…®ra risambwa riyo akabhuga, ‚ÄúKira! Nuurw…® k âm â ât â w ân â!‚Äù  
\v 26 Risambwa r…®kasingisha  âm â ât â wuyo bh âk âng ºu, r…®kar…®ra kwiraka na kumurw…®ku. 
\p  
\v 27 Abhaat â bh â âsi bhakar âg â âra bh âk âng ºu, bhakiibhuurya, ‚ÄúN…®‚Äëk…® k…®n â? Ni‚Äëmiija mahya, gan â  âbh ânaja! Rora, ana amanaga g â  âk âhaar…®ra na amasambwa, g â âsi garamwigwa.‚Äù  
\v 28 ∆ótaag…®gir…® ibhaga ir…®…®hu, abhaat â kurwa muchar â ch âsi cha Gariraaya, bhakabha bhiigwir…® amang ºana ga Y…®…®su. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arahorya abharw…®r…® bhaaru 
