\p  
\v 29 Han â bhaaruur…® mwirwaz…®r â, bhakaja hamw…®mw…® na Yaakobho na Yoohana kuhika wa Sim â âni na Andureya.  
\v 30 Han â bhaahikir…®bhu, Y…®…®su akabhuurirwa k âbha, uninabhyara Sim â âni ari munyumba ahindiir…®, murw…®r…® we ehooma.  
\v 31 Neho Y…®…®su akiisuka han â aar…®, akamugwata okobhoko, akam ân ânga. Ribhaga riyoriyo uninabhyara Sim â âni akahora, akatanga k âbhahokerya ibhyakurya. 
\p  
\v 32 Urusik â ruyo rigoroobha, han â  âbh ât â âr â bhwasirir…®, abhaat â bh â  âr âbh…®ri ruyo bhaar…® bharareetera Y…®…®su abharw…®r…®, na bhan â bhaar…® na amasambwa.  
\v 33 Abhaat â bhaaru kurwa m âr âbh…®ri rurya, bhakarumana k âr âk âng â rwi inyumba ya Sim â âni na Andureya.  
\v 34 Y…®…®su akahorya abhaat â bhaaru bhan â bhaar…® na amarw…®r…® g âg â âsi. Na akaruusha amasambwa maaru, nawe ataar…® aragatiga amasambwa k âbha gagamb…®, k â k âbha gakamenya k âbha ewe ni‚ÄëMwana wa Mungu. 
\s1 Y…®…®su ararwaz…®ra abhaat â 
\r (Ruuka 4:42‚Äë44) 
