\v 40 Rusik â r âmw…®  âm â ât â we ebhegenge akaja kwa Y…®…®su. Akahigama, akamwisasaama, ‚Äú…Ñraas…®…®g…®,  ârat âra k âmb…®ngukya!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 41 Y…®…®su akamororera …®bh…®g ângi, akagorora okobhoko kwaz…® na kumukun ºyaku umurw…®r…®, akam âbh â âr…®ra akabhuga, ‚ÄúN…®s…®…®gir…®. Bh…®ngukibhwa!‚Äù  
\v 42 Rogendo r âmw…® ebhegenge bh…®kamurw…®ku, akabh…®ng âka.  
\v 43 Y…®…®su akamorecha kwa kumuruushaho bhwang â,  
\v 44 akam âbh â âr…®ra, ‚Äú…Ñtagema k âbh â âr…®ra m â ât â ing ºana ry âry âsi. Nawe, nuuj…® wiiyeereken ºye kwa kuhaani,\f + \fr 1:44a \ft K âr…®ng ºaana ni imigir â ja Musa, \fk kuhaani \ft newe aar…® aramenyeekererya k âbha  âm â ât â abh…®ngukiibhw…® ebhegenge. \xt Rora Abharaawi 14:1‚Äë32; Amahiity â gi Imigir â 24:8. \ft K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora ring ºana \ft \+it abhakuhaani\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* na uhuruch…® ikimweso\f + \fr 1:44b \fk Ikimweso\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* ch â  âk âbh…®ngukibhwa kwaz â, ch…®mbu Musa aaswajiry…®, kwerecha abhaat â k âbha  âbh…®ngukiibhw…®.‚Äù  
\v 45 Nawe,  âm â ât â wurya akabh â âka harya, akatanga k âraar…®ka habhw…®r â ring ºana ry â  âk âh âribhwa kwaz…®. Ig âr â wa gayo, Y…®…®su akatamwa kusik…®ra habhw…®r â m âz…®mb…®ri z âz â âsi zirya. Akiikara umwene hagar…® ig ât â wa z…®mb…®ri, n â âr âbhu abhaat â kurwa mbaara z â âsi bhaar…® bharamujaku. 
\c 2  
\s1 Y…®…®su arahorya  âm â ât â w ân â akuur…® ibhiim â 
