\v 15 Y…®…®su akaja kurya ibhyakurya munyumba ya Raawi hamw…®mw…® na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®. Abharihya bha rig â âti\f + \fr 2:15 \fk Abharihya bha rig â âti\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* na abhand…® bh â  âbh âbh…® bhaar…® bhararya ibhyakurya hamw…®mw…® nabh â, k â k âbha bhaaru bhe eteemwa y…®n â bhaar…® bharamutuna.  
\v 16 Mmbe abhiija bhi imigir â bhan â bhaar…® Abhafarisaayo,\f + \fr 2:16 \fk Abhafarisaayo\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* han â bhaar â âz…® Y…®…®su ararya hamw…®mw…® na abharihya bha rig â âti na abhak âri bh â  âbh âbh…®, bhakabhuurya abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, ‚ÄúNdora ararya hamw…®mw…® na abharihya bha rig â âti na abhak âri bh â  âbh âbh…®?‚Äù 
