\v 26 Akasik…®ra mwibhuru rir…®ndu rya Mungu, ribhaga r…®n â Abhiyatari aar…® kuhaani  âm âk âr â wa Mungu, akarya …®m…®kaat…® g…®n â jat…®…®rw…® m âbh âtang…® bhwa Mungu.\f + \fr 2:26 \xt Rora 1 Samw…®ri 21:1‚Äë6.\f* ∆óm…®kaat…® g…®n â kumigir â ja Musa g…®takwenderwa kuriibhwa na abhaat â, kuruushaku bhakuhaani abheene. Nawe Daudi akarya, na akabhaha na abhak…®ndichaz…®, bh â âsi bhakarya.‚Äù  
