\p  
\v 5 Y…®…®su akabharora k âbh âr âr â, akarum…®ka mumw ây â gwaz…® ig âr â w â  âbh âk âng ºu bhwi imy ây â jabh â. Neho Y…®…®su akabh â âr…®ra  âm â ât â wurya, ‚ÄúGorora okobhoko kwaz â.‚Äù …Ñm â ât â wurya akagorora okobhoko kwaz…®, rogendo r âmw…® k âkahora!  
\v 6 Hayohayo Abhafarisaayo bharya bhakah âr âka ig ât â, bhakarumana na k âgambana na abhasakirya bha riribhita ry â  âm ât…®mi Heroode Antipaasi.\f + \fr 3:6 \fk Abhasakirya bha riribhita ry â  âm ât…®mi Heroode Antipaasi \ft bhaar…® riribhita rya Abhayaahudi r…®n â ryisiriiry…®  âbh âkangati bhwa Abharuumi muchar â chabh â. Ebho na Abhafarisaayo bhataas…®…®gir…®, nawe bh â âsi bhaar…® bhar â âbhaha komenyekana kwa Y…®…®su muchar â ch âsi, neho bhakatanga kwisiriran ºya komohya …®nz…®ra yu ukwita Y…®…®su. K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora ring ºana \ft \+it Heroode Antipaasi\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* Bhakagambana ch…®mbu bharaarich…® Y…®…®su. 
