\v 22 Abhiija bhi imigir â ja Musa, bhan â bhaaruur…® m âr âbh…®ri rwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu bhaar…® bharabhuga, ‚ÄúAtiirirw…® na Bh…®…®riz…®bhuri. Araheebha amasambwa k âbh ânaja bhwa Bh…®…®riz…®bhuri,\f + \fr 3:22 \fk Bh…®…®riz…®bhuri \ft ni‚Äëriina …®r…®nd…® rya Sh…®taani.\f*  âm âk âr â wa amasambwa!‚Äù 
