\v 26 Ar…®…®bh…® Sh…®taani ariitana na amasambwa amak…®ndichaz…®,  âbh ât…®mi bhwaz…® bh âtwan…®k…®…®n…®, bh ârat âra kwim…®…®r…®rabhw…®? Bh âtak ât âra kwim…®…®r…®ra n â âr â hasuuhu, maheene bhugwir…® k…®mw…®.  
\v 27 Atareeho  âm â ât â w ân â ak ât âra kusik…®ra munyumba y â  âm â ât â wa amanaga, na kumuruusha ebhegero bhyaz…®, ak…®…®r…® komobhoha. Areemobhohe, hayo arat âra kumuruusha ebhegero bhyaz…®. 
