\v 31 Neho unina Y…®…®su na abhahiiri bhaaz…® bhakahika, bhakiim…®…®r…®ra ig ât â wi inyumba y…®n â aar…®mu. Bhakat âma  âm â ât â abh…®r…®k…®r…® Y…®…®su, bhagamban…® neewe.  
