\v 2 Aar…® arabhiija amang ºana maaru kobherenjo. Mumiija gaaz…® aar…® arabhuga,  
\v 3 ‚ÄúMwitegeerere! Umubhusuri akaja kubhusura zimbusur â zaaz…®.\fig Umubhusuri|alt="Mpanzi" src="lb00094c.tif" size="col" loc="MRK 4:3" copy="Louise Bass ¬© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1994" ref="4:3" \fig* 
