\p  
\v 1 Y…®…®su akang ºeha k âbhabh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúN…®rabhabh â âr…®ra amaheene, bhareho abhaat â gat…® waanyu han â, bhan â bhatakukwa bhak…®…®r…® korora Umwana w â …Ñm â ât â araaza m âbh ât…®mi bhwaz…®.‚Äù 
