\v 2 Han â zaahitir…® sik â isaasabha, Y…®…®su akagega Peetero, Yaakobho na Yoohana, akaja hamw…®mw…® nabh â k âk…®g âr â …®k…®r…®…®hu bhakaja kekoro. Bhakarora Y…®…®su ariich âra ubhush â bhwaz…® m âbh âtang…® bhwabh â.  
