\v 4 Bhakahwar âka ∆ó…®riya na Musa,\f + \fr 9:4 \fk ∆ó…®riya \ft na \fk Musa \ft bhaar…® abhar â âti abhak âr â. Musa akabhakangata Abhiizira…®ri kurwa Miisiri kuja muchar â cha Izira…®ri. ∆ó…®riya aar…® ariisegwa k âbha aragar âka k â âs…®, Masiya ak…®…®r…® kuuza. \xt Rora Maraaki 4:5.\f* abhar â ât…®r…®ri bh…® …®kar…®, bharagambana na Y…®…®su. 
