\v 13 Nawe n…®rabhabh â âr…®ra k âbha, ∆ó…®riya\f + \fr 9:13a \ft Y…®…®su arar…®ng ºaan ºya \fk ∆ó…®riya \ft na Yoohana …Ñm âbhatiizi. Yoohana akakorera Y…®…®su …®nz…®ra, emeremo g…®n â Abhayaahudi bhaar…® bhariisega k âbha ∆ó…®riya arakora. \xt Rora Mataayo 11:13‚Äë14.\f* izir…®, bh â âsi bhakamokorera amabh…® g â âsi gan â bh…®…®ndir…®,\f + \fr 9:13b \xt Rora Maaroko 6:14‚Äë29.\f* ch…®mbu yandikirw…®.‚Äù 
