\p  
\v 42 Y…®…®su akang ºeha k âgamba, ‚ÄúNawe w ân â araahabhy…® w âmw…® gat…® wa abhasuuhu bhan â bhakunyiisirirya akore  âbh âbh…®, …®nyaak â yaaz…® …®rabha k âr â bh âk âng ºu. Hak…®r…®ku abhoherwe  âr âbhw…® mwig âti na korekerwa m ânyanza.  
\v 43 Okobhoko kwaz â k âraagiry…® okore  âbh âbh…®,  âk ât…®n…®. N…®‚Äëhak…®r…®ku usik…®r…® m âbh âh âru bhwa kemerano no okobhoko k âmw…®, k âk…®ra k âbha na amabhoko abh…®r…® na kuja nyaari, momorero g ân â g âtakurima. [ 
