\p  
\v 49 ‚ÄúMungu arahitya abhaat â bh â âsi m âz…®nyaak â z…®n â zituubh…®…®n…® no omorero, ncha abhaat â bhak âhaka  âm â âny â\f + \fr 9:49a \ft Abhayaahudi bhakahaka …®nyama \fk  âm â âny â \ft k âbha bhayeerye neho bharich…®. \xt Rora Abharaawi 2:13; ∆óz…®k…®…®ri 43:24.\f* k ânyama yi ikimweso y…®n â …®k…®…®r…® kurichwa.\f + \fr 9:49b \ft Ikigiriki k…®rabhuga, \fqa abhaat â bh â âsi bharatuurwa  âm â âny â no omorero.\f* 
\v 50 …Ñm â âny â n…®‚Äëm âz âmu, nawe guriibhury…®  âbh âsambaruku bhwagw…®, m ârag ât â âr…®ra k…®g âr âk…® korereke gozome naatu? Na niimw…® m âbh…® nch â  âm â âny â g ân â gugwatir…®, m âbh…® nu ubhwigwani abheene kobheene.‚Äù 
\c 10  
\s1 Y…®…®su ariija ig âr â wu ukukw…®ra n â  âk âtaana 
