\p  
\v 1 Neho Y…®…®su na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhakabh â âka Kap…®rinaumu, bhakaja muchar â cha Yudeya. Bhakah…®ta bhakaamb âka …®k…®taar â cha Yorodaani. Iyo amaribhita mak âr â ga abhaat â bhaar…® bharamwiruguura naatu, na aar…® arabhiija ch…®mbu aanarir…® kokora. 
\p  
\v 2 Mmbe, Abhafarisaayo bhakamujaku komogema. Bhakamubhuurya, ‚ÄúAw…®…®, n…®‚Äëbhwaheene umusubh…® k âtaana na m âkaaz…®?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 W â âsi akabhagarukirya, ‚ÄúMusa akabhaswaja migir âk…®?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Bhakam âgarukirya, bhakabhuga, ‚ÄúMusa akiisirirya umusubh…® amwand…®k…®r…® m âkaaz…® …®nyar âbha y â  âk âtaana.‚Äù\f + \fr 10:4 \xt Rora Amahiity â gi Imigir â 24:1.\f* 
\p  
\v 5 Y…®…®su akabhabh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúMusa akabhaand…®k…®ra riswaja riyo k â k âbha y â  âbh âk âng ºu bhwi imy ây â janyu.  
\v 6 Nawe, kw…®ma  âbh âtang…® bhwo okoteemwa …®…®s…®, ‚ÄòMungu akabh âmba umusubh…® n â  âm âkari.‚Äô\f + \fr 10:6 \xt Rora …Ñbh âtang…® 1:27.\f* 
\v 7 ‚ÄòIg âr â wa gayo, umusubh…® aratiga wiis…® na unina, aragwatana na m âkaaz…®.  
\v 8 Bhabh…®r…® bhayo bharabha m âbh…®r…® g âmw…®.‚Äô\f + \fr 10:8 \xt Rora …Ñbh âtang…® 2:24.\f* Na bhatak âbha bhabh…®r…® kwik…®, nawe n…®‚Äëm âbh…®r…® g âmw…®.  
