\v 19 Nawe nang â,  âj…®z…® imigir â ja Mungu g…®n â gikubhuga, ‚ÄòUtiita,  âtasebheeta, utiibha,  âtagobha m â ât â,  âtakangirirya,  âs â âk…® wuus â na onyoko.‚Äô\f + \fr 10:19 \xt Rora K âh âr âka 20:12‚Äë16; Amahiity â gi Imigir â 5:16‚Äë20.\f*‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 …Ñm â ât â wurya akabhuga, ‚ÄúUmwija, giyo j âsi n…®g…®gwatir…® kw…®ma mubhwana bhwan…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Y…®…®su akamorora, akam âs…®…®ga, akam âbh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúUsuuhiirw…® ekegero k…®mw…®. Nuuj…® ugury…® ebhegero bhy âsi bh…®n â  ânabhy â, zimpirya ziyo  âbhah…® abhahabh…®, na  ârabha ni ikibhumb…®k â kwa Mungu. Ak âmara uuz…® untun…®.‚Äù  
\v 22 Nawe, han â iigwir…®bhu, akar âg â âra. Akaja arumikir…® bh âk âng ºu, k â k âbha aar…® ne ebhegero bhyaru. 
\p  
\v 23 Y…®…®su akarora mbaara z â âsi, akabhabh â âr…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, ‚ÄúK ârabha k âk âng ºu k âbhaniibhi kusik…®ra m âbh ât…®mi bhwa Mungu.‚Äù  
\v 24 Abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhakar âg â âra k âmang ºana gaaz…®. Akabhabh â âr…®ra naatu, ‚ÄúAbhaana bhaan…®, morore ch…®mbu n…®‚Äëk âk âng ºu kusik…®ra m âbh ât…®mi bhwa Mungu.\f + \fr 10:24 \fk N…®‚Äëk âk âng ºu kusik…®ra m âbh ât…®mi bhwa Mungu\ft , Zibhibhuriya …®z…®nd…® z…®rabhuga, \fqa n…®‚Äëk âk âng ºu k âbhaat â bhan â bhakwisega ubhuniibhi bh ân â bhanabhw…®, kusik…®ra m âbh ât…®mi bhwa Mungu.\f* 
\v 25 N…®‚Äëk âny â âhu …®ngamiya k âh…®ta mwibhanga ryi isindan â, k âk…®ra umuniibhi kusik…®ra m âbh ât…®mi bhwa Mungu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhakar âg â âra bh âk âng ºu kwa ring ºana riyo. Bhaar…® bhariibhuurya abheene kobheene, ‚ÄúNang â, n…®‚Äëw…®…®w…® w ân â ak ât âra k âsabhurwa?‚Äù 
