\v 29 Y…®…®su akabhuga, ‚ÄúN…®rabhabh â âr…®ra amaheene,  âm â ât â w ân â atigir…® inyumba, umwabh â, umusubhaati, unina, wiis…®, abhaana, hamw…® …®m…®g ând â, ig âr â waan…® ni ig âr â w…® ∆óng ºana ∆ónz âmu,  
\v 30 Mungu aramoha bhyaru bh âk âng ºu k âk…®ra bhirya. Nang â kwibhaga r…®n â, aras âng ºaana zinyumba, bhaumwabh â, abhasubhaati, bhaunina, abhaana n…® …®m…®g ând â. Hamw…®mw…® na gayo g â âsi, arabha n…® …®nyaak â. N…® …®…®s…® y…®n â ikuuza, aras âng ºaana  âbh âh âru bhwa kemerano.  
\v 31 Nawe, abhaat â bhaaru bhan â bhakusuukwa ribhaga r…®n â, bhatakusuukwa ribhaga r…®n â rikuuza. Na bhan â bhatakusuukwa ribhaga r…®n â, bharasuukwa ribhaga r…®n â rikuuza.‚Äù 
\s1 Y…®…®su aroongera k âgamb…®ra ukukwa nu ukury âka kwaz…® 
