\p  
\v 32 Han â Y…®…®su na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhaar…® k ânz…®ra kuja m âr âbh…®ri rwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu, Y…®…®su aar…® arakangata m âbh âtang…® bhwabh â. Abh…®…®ga bha Y…®…®su bhakar âg â âra, na abhaat â abhand…® bhan â bhaar…® bharamutuna, bhaar…® nu ubhw âbha. Y…®…®su akabhabh…®r…®k…®ra naatu rusiz â abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® ikumi na bhabh…®r…®, akatanga k âbhabh â âr…®ra gan â gareemobhone.  
\v 33 Akabhuga, ‚ÄúRora, t âraja Y…®rusar…®…®mu. Iyo, Umwana w â …Ñm â ât â aragwatwa na kuhirwa k âbhak âr â bha abhakuhaani na abhiija bhi imigir â ja Musa. Bhayo bharat…®n…®ra iitw…®, na bharamuhira k âBharuumi.  
\v 34 Abhaat â bhayo bharamorega na kumutw…®ra amat…®. Bharamotema …®m…®zariti na kumwita. Nawe, urusik â rwa katat â, arary âka.‚Äù 
