\v 35 Yaakobho na Yoohana, abhaana bha Zebhedaayo, bhakiisuk…®ra Y…®…®su, bhakam âbh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúUmwija, t ârasabha otokorere ry âry âsi r…®n â t âr…®…®k âsabh…®.‚Äù 
