\v 39 Bhakam âgarukirya, ‚ÄúT ârat âra.‚Äù 
\p Y…®…®su akabhabh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúMaheene, m ârakinyw…®ra ekekombe ch…® …®nyaak â y…®n â iny…® n…®k ânyaaka, na k âbha ni ibhaga ik âng ºu nchi iryan…®.\f + \fr 10:39 \fk K âbha ni ibhaga ik âng ºu nchi iryan…® \ft kuKigiriki n…®‚Äë\fqa m ârabhatiizwa ch…®mbu iny…® nabhatiizirw…®.\f* 
\v 40 Nawe kwikara  âr âbhaara rwan…® rwu ubhury â hamw…® rw â  âbh âm âsi g…®tar…® emeremo jan…® kubhiisiririrya. Umweya guyo n…®‚Äëk â bhan â Mungu amarir…® kokonzera.‚Äù 
\p  
