\v 17 Ak âmara Y…®…®su akabhiija, akabhuga, ‚Äú∆ótaandikirw…® m âMaand…®k â Amar…®ndu k âbha, ‚ÄòInyumba yaan…® …®rabha ya amasabhi k âbhaat â bhi ibhyar â bhy âsi?‚Äô\f + \fr 11:17a \xt Rora Isaaya 56:7.\f* Nawe imw…®, m ây…®k ârir…® k âbha ribhigi rya abhasaakuri!‚Äù\f + \fr 11:17b \xt Rora Y…®r…®miya 7:11.\f* 
