\v 22 Y…®…®su akabhabh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúMwisiriry…® Mungu.  
\v 23 N…®rabhabh â âr…®ra amaheene, ar…®…®bh…®  âm â ât â ariisirirya na ataana mak…®bhw…® mumw ây â gwaz…®, r…®n â araabhug…® r…®rakorwa. Arat âra k âbh â âr…®ra …®k…®g âr â k…®n â, ‚ÄòIh…®ka witaash…® m ânyanza,‚Äô na gayo garakorwa.  
