\p  
\v 1 Y…®…®su akatanga k âgambana na abhakangati bha Abhayaahudi bharya kobherenjo. Akabhuga, ‚ÄúKwar…® n â  âm â ât â w âmw…® w ân â aarimir…®  âm âg ând â gw…® …®m…®zabhiibhu. Akag âbhag…®ra, akatuka ikisima chu ukugund…®k…®ra …®m…®zabhiibhu girya. Ak â âmbaka …®k…®k âng â …®k…®r…®…®hu cha abhariibhi m âm âg ând â. Akak â âdishirya abharimi. Ewe akaja ichar â …®k…®nd…®.  
\v 2 Ribhaga ryu ukutwa z…®zabhiibhu r…®kahika, akam ât âma w âmw…® wa bhamb â âsa bhaaz…® k âbharimi bharya, bhamohe esondo yaaz…® ya z…®zabhiibhu kurwa m âm âg ând â gwaz…®.  
