\v 4 W â  âm âg ând â akat âma mb â âsa  âw ând…® k âbharimi. W â âsi bhakamotema na k âm ânyahaara kumutw…®, na komokorera k…®bh…® bh âk âng ºu.  
\v 5 Akat âma mb â âsa waaz…®  âw ând…®, w â âsi abharimi bhakamwita. Akabhat âma bhamb â âsa bhaaz…® abhand…® bhaaru. Abharimi bharya bhakabhatema, abhand…® bhakabhiita.  
\v 6 W â  âm âg ând â akasaaga na w âmw…®, umwana waaz…®  âm âs…®…®gwa. ∆ót…®n…®r â akam ât âma k âbharimi bharya, akiiseega, ‚ÄòBharam âs â âka umwana waan…®.‚Äô 
