\v 9 ‚ÄúNang â w â  âm âg ând â wuyo arakorabhw…®? Araaza na kubhiita abharimi bharya, n â  âm âg ând â guyo, arabhaha abhaat â abhand…®.  
\v 10 Nang â, m âk…®…®r…® kosoma Amaand…®k â gan â? 
