\p  
\v 12 Abhak âr â bha abhakuhaani, abhiija bhi imigir â ja Musa na abhak âr â, bhakoobhoora k âbha ekerenjo kiyo nebho k…®k âgamb…®ra. Neho bhakeenda kumugwata, nawe k â k âbha bhak â âbhaha riribhita rya abhaat â, bhakamutiga, bhakabh â âka. 
