\v 13 Neho abhak âr â bha Abhayaahudi, bhakat âma Abhafarisaayo obhorebhe na abhasakirya bha riribhita ry â  âm ât…®mi Heroode Antipaasi, bhahaaty…® Y…®…®su k âr…®ng ºaana na amang ºana gaaz…® umwene.  
