\v 9 ‚ÄúNawe imw…®, mwiyangar…®r…® bh âk âng ºu. Abhaat â bharabhahira k âbhakangati na abhat…®mi m âmarwaz…®r â. Bharabhahira m âbh âtang…® bhwa abhakangati na abhat…®mi ig âr â waan…®. Moreenderwa k âbha abham…®ny…®…®k…®r…®ri bhaan…® m âbh âtang…® bhwabh â.  
