\v 3 Ribhaga riyo Y…®…®su aar…® Bh…®taniya, wa Sim â âni w ân â aar…® ne ebhegenge. Han â aar…® kwigari, akaaza  âm âkari w âmw…® ani ichupa …®nz âmu ya amaguta ga narid â. Amaguta gayo gaar…® gi iguri ik âr â, na garareetya bhwaheene. Akat…®na umunywa gwi ichupa, akiit âr âr…®ra Y…®…®su kumutw…®.  
\v 4 Abhaat â obhorebhe bhan â bhaar…® munyumba yirya, bhakiigatana. Bhakatanga k âgamba abheene kobheene, ‚ÄúNdora arasarya amaguta amaz âmu gan â?  
\v 5 Amaguta gan â gakeenderwa kuguribhwa zidinaari magana atat â,\f + \fr 14:5 \fk Zidinaari magana atat â \ft zaar…® n…®‚Äëmarihi g â  âm â ât â kumwaka g âmw…®.\f* na k âhaabhwa abhahabh…®.‚Äù Bhakahaar…®ra  âm âkari wurya. 
\p  
\v 6 Nawe Y…®…®su akabhuga, ‚ÄúMumutig…®. Ndora m âram ânyaacha? R…®n â  âm âkari w ân â ank âr…®…®r…® ni‚Äëz âmu.  
\v 7 Abhahabh…® m ânabh â sik â z â âsi. M ârat âra k âbhakorera amaz âmu ribhaga ry âry âsi r…®n â m âs…®…®gir…®. Nawe iny…® n…®tak âbha na niimw…® sik â z â âsi.  
\v 8 …Ñm âkari w ân â ak ârir…® r…®n â ak ât âra. Akangatir…® k âhaka  âm âbh…®r…® gwan…® amaguta ig âr â wa amabh…®…®ka gaan…®.  
\v 9 N…®rabhabh â âr…®ra amaheene, h âh â âsi mubhyar â han â abhaat â bhak âbha bhararwaza ∆óng ºana ∆ónz âmu, bharabha bharagamba r…®n â  âm âkari w ân â aak ârir…®, kumuhiita.‚Äù 
