\v 10 Neho Yuuda Isikariy â âti, w âmw…® wa abh…®…®ga ikumi na bhabh…®r…® bha Y…®…®su bharya, akaja kumwich âra k âbhak âr â bha abhakuhaani, abheereche …®nz…®ra yu ukugwata Y…®…®su.  
\v 11 Han â bhiigwir…® amang ºana gayo, bhakazomerwa bh âk âng ºu. Bhakiisiriran ºya nawe k âbha bharamoha zimpirya. Neho Yuuda akatanga komohya umweya  âm âz âmu gu ukumwich âra. 
