\v 13 Neho Y…®…®su akat âma abh…®…®ga bhabh…®r…®, akabhabh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúMuj…® m âr âbh…®ri rwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu, iyo m ârahunana nu umusubh…® w âmw…® ag…®gir…® inywa, mumutun…®.  
\v 14 Munyumba y…®n â ariisik…®r…®, muj…® m âm âbh â âr…®r…® umwene nyumba, ‚ÄòUmwija arasabha utwereche …®gat…® han â araar…®…®r…® ∆ópasaka hamw…®mw…® na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®.‚Äô‚Ää  
\v 15 Neho umwene nyumba arabheerecha …®gat…® ahak âr â mogorofa, hak ânzirw…® k…®mw…®. Mototengere muyo, t âr…®…®r…® ∆ópasaka.‚Äù  
\v 16 Abh…®…®ga bharya bhakabh â âka, bhakaja m âr âbh…®ri rwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu. Bhakabhona g â âsi gar…® ch…®mbu Y…®…®su aabhabhuuriir…®, bhakatenga ibhyakurya bhy…® ∆ópasaka.\f + \fr 14:16 \xt Rora K âh âr âka 12:3‚Äë11.\f* 
