\v 17 Han â ryahikir…® rigoroobha, Y…®…®su akahika munyumba yirya hamw…®mw…® na abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® ikumi na bhabh…®r…® bharya.  
\v 18 Han â bhaar…® bhararya, Y…®…®su akabhuga, ‚ÄúN…®rabhabh â âr…®ra amaheene, w âmw…® waanyu, w â âsi ararya hamw…®mw…® na niiny…®, aranyiich âra.‚Äù 
