\v 25 N…®rabhabh â âr…®ra amaheene k âbha, n…®takunywa naatu idivaayi kuhika han â nikunywa bhuhya m âbh ât…®mi bhwa Mungu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ak âmara bhak…®…®mba iry…®mb â ryu ukukumya Mungu. Bhakabh â âka hayo, bhakaja k âk…®g âr â ch…® ∆óm…®z…®yituuni. 
