\p  
\v 27 Han â bhaar…® k ânz…®ra, Y…®…®su akabh â âr…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, ‚ÄúImw âsi m âraang ºosa k âgan â gak âh âr âka. Garabha ch…®mbu Mungu aagambir…® m âMaand…®k â Amar…®ndu, 
\q1 ‚ÄòN…®ramwita umuriisha, 
\q1 na z…®ng º ându zaaz…® z…®ranyaragana.‚Äô\f + \fr 14:27 \xt Rora Zaakariya 13:7.\f* 
