\p  
\v 43 Han â Y…®…®su aar…® ak…®…®r…® aragamba gayo, hayohayo Yuuda, w âmw…® wa abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® ikumi na bhabh…®r…®, akahika na abhaat â bhaaru, bhan â bhagwatiriir…® amasabha na amarungu m âmabhoko. Abhaat â bhayo bhakarwa k âbhak âr â bha abhakuhaani, abhiija bhi imigir â ja Musa na abhakaruka.  
\v 44 Yuuda w ân â iichurir…® Y…®…®su, aar…® abhah…®…®r…® ich…®r…®k…®n ºy â, arabhuga, ‚Äú…Ñm â ât â w ân â n…®raahumbat…®, momenye, newe. Mumugwat…® na k âbh â âka nawe, m âm ât â âr…® mozemboko.‚Äù 
