\v 47 Neho,  âm â ât â w âmw…® m âbharya bhan â bhiimiiriir…® harya hamw…®mw…® na Y…®…®su, akasohora risabha ryaz…®, akat…®na  âk âtw…® kwa mb â âsa wa kuhaani  âm âk âr â kutu. 
\p  
\v 48 Y…®…®su akabh â âr…®ra abhaat â bharya, ‚ÄúNdora mwizir…® na amasabha na amarungu, mungwat…® iny…®, ncha abhaat â bhan â bhakuja kugwata  âm âsaakuri?  
\v 49 K…®rakabhu naar…® hamw…®mw…® na niimw…®, niriija mwihekaaru, m âtaangwatir…®. Nawe gan â g â âsi gak ârirw…® korereke gan â gaandikirw…® m âMaand…®k â Amar…®ndu, gakorwe.‚Äù\f + \fr 14:49 \xt Rora Maaroko 14:27; Zaakariya 13:7.\f* 
\p  
\v 50 Neho abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bh â âsi bhakaryara, bhakamutiga.  
