\v 52 nawe akas âs âbh âka m âmabhoko, akatiga umwenda gwaz…®, akaryara mwega ar…® t â âh â. 
\s1 Y…®…®su m âbh âtang…® bhwi ichandar â …®k…®k âr â cha Abhayaahudi 
\r (Mataayo 26:57‚Äë68; Ruuka 22:54‚Äë55, 63‚Äë71; Yoohana 18:13‚Äë14, 19‚Äë24) 
\p  
\v 53 Neho abhaat â bharya bhakahira Y…®…®su kwa kuhaani  âm âk âr â. Bhakiibhiringa harya abhak âr â bh â âsi bha abhakuhaani,\f + \fr 14:53 \fk Abhakuhaani\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* abhakaruka na abhiija bhi imigir â ja Musa.  
\v 54 Peetero akabha aratuna Y…®…®su kwa kore. Akaja, akasik…®ra mwigoobhe rya kuhaani  âm âk âr â. Akiikara murya hamw…®mw…® na abhariibhi bha kuhaani  âm âk âr â, akabha aroota omorero. 
\p  
\v 55 Abhak âr â bha abhakuhaani ni ichandar â\f + \fr 14:55 \fk Ichandar â\ft . K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora Ikiniibhasa.\f* ch âsi bhakatanga komohya obhomenyeekererya bhw â  âk âgamba Y…®…®su, korereke bham ât…®n…®r…® na kumwita. Nawe, bhataar…® bharabhona obhomenyeekererya bhw âbhw âsi.  
\v 56 Abhaat â bhaaru bhaar…® bharahurucha obhomenyeekererya bhw â  âr âr…®m…® k âgamba Y…®…®su, nawe obhomenyeekererya bhwabh â bh âtaar…® bhuriigwana.  
\v 57 Ak âmara, abhaat â abhand…® obhorebhe bhakiim…®…®r…®ra, bhakahurucha obhomenyeekererya bhw â  âr âr…®m…®. Bhaar…® bharabhuga,  
\v 58 ‚ÄúItw…® abheene tukiigwa  âm â ât â w ân â arabhuga, ‚ÄòIny…® n…®ragwisha rihekaaru rya Mungu r…®n â abhaat â bh â âmbakir…®. Na n…®r â âmbaka …®r…®nd…® kwa sik â isat âbhu. Rihekaaru riyo r…®tak â âmbakwa na abhaat â.‚Äô‚Ää‚Äù  
\v 59 N â âr âbhu, obhomenyeekererya bhwabh â bh âtaar…® bhuriigwana. 
\p  
\v 60 Ak âmara kuhaani  âm âk âr â akiim…®…®r…®ra embere wi ichandar â. Akabhuurya Y…®…®su, ‚ÄúAw…®…®,  âtak âgarukirya ing ºana ry âry âsi, r…®n â abhaat â bhan â bhak âk âgamba?‚Äù  
\v 61 Nawe Y…®…®su akakira kiri, ataagambir…® ing ºana ry âry âsi. Kuhaani  âm âk âr â akang ºeha kumubhuurya, ‚ÄúAw…® ni‚ÄëKiriisit â, Umwana wa Mungu w ân â akukumibhwa?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 62 Y…®…®su akagarukirya, ‚ÄúIny…® newe. Na niimw…® m ârarora Umwana w â …Ñm â ât â ik…®…®r…®  âr âbhaara rwu ubhury â rwa Mungu wa Amanaga.\f + \fr 14:62a \xt Rora Zabhuri 110:1.\f* Na m âramorora araaza m âmasaar â kurwa mwisaar â.‚Äù\f + \fr 14:62b \xt Rora Dany…®ri 7:13.\f* 
\p  
\v 63 Neho kuhaani  âm âk âr â akatarand âra zengebho zaaz…® kwerecha asaayir…® bh âk âng ºu, akabhuga, ‚ÄúN…®‚Äëbhamenyeekereryak…® bhan â tukwenda?  
\v 64 Mwigwir…® abheene ch…®mbu akorega Mungu! Nang â imw…®, m ârabhugabhw…®?‚Äù Ichandar â ch âsi k…®kabhuga areenderwa iitw…®. 
\p  
\v 65 Abhand…® bhakatanga kumutw…®ra amat…®, komobhoha mubhush â na komotema ibhikundi, …®n â bharam âbh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúRootorera n…®‚Äëw…®…®w…® w ân â ak ât…®mir…®!‚Äù Na abhariibhi bhan â bhaar…® harya, bhakamogega, bhakamotema. 
\s1 Peetero araanga Y…®…®su 
\r (Mataayo 26:69‚Äë75; Ruuka 22:56‚Äë62; Yoohana 18:15‚Äë18, 25‚Äë27) 
\p  
\v 66 Ribhaga riyo ry âsi, Peetero aar…® mwigoobhe, iyaas…® wi ichumba han â Y…®…®su aar…® arabhuuribhwa. Akaaza omohocha w âmw…® w…® …®k…®kari wa kuhaani  âm âk âr â.  
\v 67 Akarora Peetero aroota omorero, akamomogorera. Akam âbh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúNa naaw…® waar…® hamw…®mw…® na Y…®…®su, …Ñm ânazar…®…®ti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 68 Nawe Peetero akaanga arabhuga, ‚ÄúN…®t…®…®z…® na n…®takwigwa gan â  âk âgamba!‚Äù Akaja kukishoko cha rigoobhe. Ribhaga riryarirya, ekorokoome …®kagamba. 
\p  
\v 69 …Ñm âkari wuyo akarora Peetero, akatanga k âbh â âr…®ra abhaat â bhan â bhiimiiriir…® harya, ‚Äú…Ñm â ât â w ân â w â âsi ar…® hamw…®mw…® nabh â.‚Äù  
\v 70 Nawe Peetero akaanga kwik…®. 
\p R…®kah…®ta ibhaga isuuhu, abhaat â bhan â bhiimiiriir…® harya, bhakam âbh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúAmaheene aw…® n…®‚Äëw âmw…® waabh â, k â k âbha na naaw…® M âgariraaya  âr…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 71 Nawe, Peetero akatanga kwihiimirirya na kwirah…®ra, ‚Äú…Ñm â ât â w ân â m âk âgamba, iny…® n…®tamw…®z…®!‚Äù  
\v 72 Hayohayobhu, ekorokoome …®kagamba rwa kabh…®r…®. Ribhaga riyo, Peetero akahiita ring ºana rya Y…®…®su r…®n â aamubhuuriir…®, ‚ÄúEkorokoome …®k…®…®r…® k âgamba manga kabh…®r…®,  ârabha  ânyangir…® katat â.‚Äù Peetero han â is…®…®gir…® gayo, akar…®ra. 
\c 15  
\s1 Y…®…®su arahirwa kwa Piraato 
\r (Mataayo 27:1‚Äë2, 11‚Äë14; Ruuka 23:1‚Äë3; Yoohana 18:28‚Äë38) 
\p  
\v 1 Han â bhw…®rir…®bhu, ichandar â ch âsi cha abhak âr â bha abhakuhaani, abhakaruka na abhiija bhi imigir â ja Musa, bhakiisiriran ºya. Bhakabhoha Y…®…®su, bhakamuhira kwa Piraato. 
