\p  
\v 6 Musigukuru y…® ∆ópasaka, Piraato aar…® ni isim âka yu ukumutig âr âk…®ra omobhohwa w âmw…®, w ân â abhaat â bhaar…® bhak âsabha atazurw…®.  
\v 7 Ribhaga riyo mokebhoho bhaar…®mu abhaat â bhan â bhiichurir…® na kokora ubhwiti mubhwangi bhwabh â. W âmw…® wa abhiiti bhayo aar…® arabhirikirwa Bharaabha.  
\v 8 Riribhita ik âr â rya abhaat â bhakaja kwa Piraato, bhakam âsabha abhataz âr…®r…® omobhohwa w âmw…®, ch…®mbu aanarir…® kokora. 
\p  
