\v 10 Akagambabhu k â k âbha akamenya k âbha abhak âr â bha abhakuhaani bhakamuhira Y…®…®su kwewe ig âr â we eng ºeera yaabh âbhu.  
\v 11 Nawe abhak âr â bha abhakuhaani bhakasiigirirya riribhita rya abhaat â rirya, r…®kasabha Piraato abhataz âr…®r…® Bharaabha.  
\v 12 Piraato akabhabhuurya naatu, ‚ÄúMmbe, moreenda nekorebhw…®  âm â ât â w ân â mukubhuga n…®‚Äëm ât…®mi wa Abhayaahudi?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Abhaat â bh â âsi bhakar…®g…®sa bharabhuga, ‚ÄúM âm âbhamb…® k âm âsarabha!‚Äù 
