\p Neho ebho bhakang ºeha k âr…®g…®sa bh âk âng ºu, bharabhuga, ‚ÄúM âm âbhamb…® k âm âsarabha!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Piraato kwa k âs…®…®ga k âsambarucha riribhita rya abhaat â riyo, akabhataz âr…®ra Bharaabha. Akaswaja abhasirikar…® korereke bhateme Y…®…®su …®m…®zariti, bhakamotema. Ak âmara akamuhurucha bham âbhamb…® k âm âsarabha. 
\s1 Abhasirikar…® bharasiihya Y…®…®su 
