\v 16 Abhasirikar…® bhakagega Y…®…®su, bhakaja nawe mwik âr â rya Piraato. Bhakabhiringa riribhita ik âr â rya abhasirikar…®.  
\v 17 Bhakamwibhohya engebho ya zambaraaw…®. Bhakagisa …®k…®r âng â cha amahwa, bhakamwibhohya kumutw…®.  
