\v 20 Han â bhaamarir…® kumusiihya, bhakamuruusha engebho ya zambaraaw…® yirya, na kumwibhohya naatu zengebho zaaz…®. Bhakamuhira bham âbhamb…® k âm âsarabha. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arabhambwa k âm âsarabha 
\r (Mataayo 27:32‚Äë44; Ruuka 23:26‚Äë43; Yoohana 19:17‚Äë27) 
\p  
\v 21 K ânz…®ra, bhakarumana n â  âm â ât â w ân â aar…® ak âh…®ta k âr âbh…®ri kurwa m âm âg ând â, iriina ryaz…® Sim â âni kurwa Kireene. …Ñm â ât â wuyo aar…® wiis…® Ar…®kizanda na Ruuf â. Abhasirikar…® bhakam âhat…®ka agege  âm âsarabha gwa Y…®…®su.  
\v 22 Bhakahira Y…®…®su han â haabhirikiirw…® G ârig â âta, enzobhooro yaku n…®‚Äëk âK…®hanga chu Umutw…®.  
\v 23 Bhakaha Y…®…®su idivaayi y…®n â bhaasang…®…®n ºy…® n â  âm ât…®,\f + \fr 15:23 \fk …Ñm ât…® \ft guyo g ârabhirikirwa man…®man…®, bhakamoha ig âr â wo okomorega, gwar…® g ân â  âbh âr âr â.\f* nawe ewe akaanga kunywa.  
\v 24 Neho bhakam âbhamba k âm âsarabha, na bhakatwana zengebho zaaz…®. Bhakakora ubhwit â âri kuhitya w…®…®w…® aragega engebhok…®.  
\v 25 Ribhaga r…®n â bhaam âbhambir…®, yaar…® …®sa isat â ritabh â âri. 
\p  
\v 26 Bhakat â âra ig âr â w â  âm âsarabha amaand…®k â g â  âbh âbh…® bhwaz…®, gaar…® garabhuga, ‚Äú\sc …Ñm ât…®mi wa Abhayaahudi\sc*.‚Äù  
\v 27 Bhakam âbhamba na abhasaakuri bhabh…®r…® k âm…®sarabha,  âw âmw…®  âr âbhaara rwaz…® rwu ubhury â n â  âw ând…®  âr âbhaara rw â  âbh âm âsi. [ 
\v 28 Neho gakakunana Amaand…®k â Amar…®ndu gan â gakubhuga, ‚ÄúAkabharwa hamw…®mw…® na abhak âri bha amabh…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 15:28 \xt Rora Isaaya 53:12.\f*] 
\p  
\v 29 Abhaat â bhan â bhaar…® bhak âh…®ta k ânz…®ra hayo, bhakam ât âka, bharasingisha imitw…® jabh â bharabhuga, ‚ÄúAa! Aw…®, w ân â akwasha rihekaaru na kury âmbaka kuzisik â isat â,  
\v 30 nang â, wiituury…® aumwene, wiik…® k âm âsarabha!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Na abhak âr â bha abhakuhaani na abhiija bhi imigir â ja Musa bh â âsi hamw…®mw…®, bhakamorega bharabhuga, ‚ÄúAkasabh âra abhand…®, nawe atak ât âra kwisabh âra umwene!  
\v 32 Ang â, abhugir…® k âbha newe Kiriisit â,  âm ât…®mi wa Abhiizira…®ri. Nang â iik…® k âm âsarabha, korereke tomorore nu ukumwisirirya.‚Äù Na abhaat â bhan â bhaabhambirw…® hamw…®mw…® nawe, bh â âsi bhakam ât âka. 
\s1 Uruku rwa Y…®…®su 
\r (Mataayo 27:45‚Äë56; Ruuka 23:44‚Äë49; Yoohana 19:28‚Äë30) 
\p  
\v 33 K âtang…®ra z…®…®sa isaasabha umwise kuhika z…®…®sa kenda, …®kabha ikiirimya kuchar â ch âsi.  
\v 34 Neho z…®…®sa kenda, Y…®…®su akar…®ra kwiraka ik âr â arabhuga, ‚Äú∆ór â âyi! ∆ór â âyi! Raama sabhakitaani?‚Äù Enzobhooro yaku ni‚Äë‚ÄúMungu waan…®, Mungu waan…®, ndora untigir…®?‚Äù\f + \fr 15:34 \xt Rora Zabhuri 22:1.\f* 
\p  
\v 35 Abhaat â obhorebhe gat…® wa bhan â bhiimiiriir…® harya, han â bhiigwir…® gan â ak âgamba, bhakabhuga, ‚ÄúMwigw…® bhamura, arabh…®r…®k…®ra ∆ó…®riya  âm âr â ât…®r…®ri wa Mungu.‚Äù\f + \fr 15:35 \ft ∆ó…®riya aragambwa han â k â k âbha Abhayaahudi bhaaru bhaar…® bhariisirirya k âbha ∆ó…®riya atakuur…®, nawe Mungu akamogega k â âs…® han â m âh âru na kuja nawe mwisaar â. Na bhaar…® bhariisega k âbha ∆ó…®riya aragar âka kwik…® k â âs…®. \xt Rora 2 Abhat…®mi 2:11; Maraaki 4:5.\f* 
\v 36 …Ñm â ât â w âmw…® akaryara bhwang â kotobheka ripuupya m âmarwa amar âr â gi idivaayi, akabhohera kwik âr…® rir…®…®hu. Akar…®n ânga ig âr â, akaha Y…®…®su anyw…®. …Ñm â ât â wuyo akabhuga, ‚ÄúMutig…® torore ar…®…®bh…® ∆ó…®riya araaza kumwicha k âm âsarabha hayo!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Y…®…®su akar…®ra kwiraka ik âr â, akatin ºya.  
\v 38 Ripaziya ryu ukusik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu mwihekaaru\f + \fr 15:38 \fk Ripaziya ryu ukusik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu mwihekaaru \ft riyo ryar…® mwihekaaru, r…®rak…®nga abhaat â bhatasik…®ra Ahar…®ndu ha Ahar…®ndu, han â ubhw…®r â bhwa Mungu bhwik…®…®r…®. \xt Rora Abh…®…®bhuraaniya 6:19, 10:19‚Äë22. \ft K âmarag…®r…®ra bh âk âng ºu, rora ring ºana \ft \+it rihekaaru\+it* muKiniibhasa.\f* r…®kabhaar âka, mbaara ibh…®r…® kuhika iyaas…®.\fig Ripaziya r…®bhaarukir…® mwihekaaru|alt="Pazia limepasuka hekaluni" src="lb00265c.tif" size="col" loc="MRK 15:38" copy="Louise Bass ¬© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1994" ref="15:38" \fig* 
\v 39 …Ñm âk âr â wa abhasirikar…® w ân â aar…® imiiriir…® embere wa Y…®…®su, han â aar â âz…® ch…®mbu Y…®…®su akukwa, akabhuga, ‚ÄúHeene  âm â ât â w ân â aar…® Umwana wa Mungu!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 40 Bhaareho abhakari bhan â bhaar â âz…® kwa kore. Gat…® waabh â aareho Mariyamu wa Magidarena, Saroome na Mariyamu unina Yaakobho umusuuhu na Yoose.  
\v 41 Abhakari bhayo bhaar…® bhamutunir…® na kohokerya Y…®…®su han â aar…® muchar â cha Gariraaya. Bhaareho na abhakari abhand…® bhaaru bhan â bhagiir…® hamw…®mw…® nawe Y…®rusar…®…®mu. 
