\p  
\v 1 Han â urusik â rw â  âbh ât â âr â rwahitir…®, Mariyamu wa Magidarena, Saroome na Mariyamu unina Yaakobho, bhakag âra amaguta go okoreetya, bhaj…® bhahak…® …®k…®t ând â.  
