\v 3 Han â bhaar…® m ânz…®ra, bhakatanga kwibhuurya, ‚ÄúN…®‚Äëw…®…®w…® w ân â akuturuushirya riibhw…® rirya kukisik â chi imbih…®ra?‚Äù  
\v 4 Nawe han â bhaahikir…®, bhakarora riibhw…® rirya rihiringitiibhw…®, riri rusiz â, na ryar…® ik âr â bh âk âng ºu. 
\p  
\v 5 Han â bhaasikiir…® mumbih…®ra, bhakiitacha korora mumura w âmw…® ibh âhir…® engebho nz…®r â. Iik…®…®r…®  âr âbhaara rwu ubhury â rwi imbih…®ra.  
\v 6 Neho akabhabh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúM ât â âbhaha! N…®…®z…® m âramohya Y…®…®su wa Nazar…®…®ti, w ân â aabhambirw…®. Atar…® han â! Aryukir…®, morore han â bhaam ât…®…®r…®.  
\v 7 Muj…® m âbh â âr…®r…® abh…®…®ga bhaaz…®, k…®nda Peetero k âbha, Y…®…®su arabhakangat…®ra kuja Gariraaya. Iyo neyo m âraamorore ch…®mbu aabhabhuuriir…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 16:7 \xt Rora Maaroko 14:28.\f* 
\v 8 Han â bhiigwir…®bhu, bhakatanga kurigita kwa bhw âbha na k âr âg â âra. Bhakarwa mumbih…®ra hayo mwega. Bhataabhuuriir…® m â ât â w âw â âsi, k â k âbha bhak â âbhaha. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arahwar âk…®ra Mariyamu wa Magidarena 
