\p [ 
\v 9 Han â Y…®…®su aaryukir…® ritabh â âri urusik â rw â  âbh âtang…® rwi inyuma, akamuhwar âk…®ra hinga Mariyamu wa Magidarena, w ân â aar…® amuruushiry…® amasambwa muhungat…®.  
\v 10 Mariyamu akaja, akabhabh â âr…®ra bhan â bhaar…® hamw…®mw…® na Y…®…®su, na ribhaga riyo bhaar…® bharar…®ra na kwarama.  
