\v 12 Urusik â ruyoruyo, Y…®…®su akahwar âk…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bhabh…®r…®, aar…® ni ikisisi k…®nd…®. Abh…®…®ga bharya bhaar…® k ânz…®ra bhararwa Y…®rusar…®…®mu.  
\v 13 Bh â âsi bhakagar âka k âbhabh â âr…®ra abhak…®ndichabh â, nawe abh…®…®ga bhayo bhatiisiriiry…®. 
\s1 Y…®…®su arahwar âk…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® 
\r (Mataayo 28:16‚Äë20; Ruuka 24:36‚Äë49; Yoohana 20:19‚Äë23; Amahocha ga Abhatumwa 1:6‚Äë8) 
\p  
\v 14 M ât…®n…®r â, Y…®…®su akahwar âk…®ra abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® ikumi na w âmw…®, han â bhaar…® kwigari bhararya. Akabharecha k âbh âk âng ºu bhwi imy ây â jabh â, k â k âbha bhaangir…® kwisirirya ga abhak…®ndichabh â bhan â bhaar â âz…® Y…®…®su han â aaryukir…® m âbhaku.  
\v 15 Neho akabhabh â âr…®ra, ‚ÄúMuj…® mubhyar â bhy âsi, m âbharwaz…®r…® abhaat â bh â âsi ∆óng ºana yaan…® ∆ónz âmu.  
\v 16 W ân â w â âsi ariisiriry…® na k âbhatiizwa, arasabhurwa. Nawe, w ân â araang…® kwisirirya, aratinirwa.  
\v 17 Abhaat â bhan â bhariisiriry…®, bharakora ibhy…®r…®k…®n ºy â bh…®n â, ukuruusha amasambwa k âbhaat â kuriina ryan…®,  âk âgamba …®bh…®gamb â ibhihya,  
\v 18 bhangagwata nzoka hamw…® bhanganywa kegero cha kwita, k…®tak âbhanyahaara. Bharabha bharat â âra amabhoko gaabh â k âbharw…®r…®, bh â âsi bharahora.‚Äù 
