\p  
\v 19 Han â …Ñm âk âr â Y…®…®su aamarir…® k âgambana nabh â, Mungu akamogega kuja mwisaar â. Akiikara  âr âbhaara rwu ubhury â rwa Mungu.  
\v 20 Abh…®…®ga bhaaz…® bharya bhakabh â âka, bhakaja kurwaza ∆óng ºana ∆ónz âmu hagero h â âsi. …Ñm âk âr â Y…®…®su aar…® arabhaha amanaga go okokora ibhy…®r…®k…®n ºy â. N…®mbu aar…® aramenyeekererya amang ºana gayo k âbha n…®‚Äëga amaheene.]